---
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="border-b border-bone-100 px-8 py-16 sm:px-10 sm:py-20 lg:px-15 lg:py-24"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-20">
      <!-- Left — Section label + headline -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-bone-300 bg-cream-100 px-3 py-1">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-honey-200"></span>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-stone-600">About me</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-outfit text-4xl font-black leading-tight text-stone-900 sm:text-5xl">
          Where business acumen
          <span class="text-honey-200"> meets code.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-stone-600">
          I'm a Web Developer based in London with a Computer Science background and a career
          path that took me through banking, financial consulting, and sales management before
          landing in tech. That journey wasn't a detour — it was a foundation.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-stone-600">
          At <strong class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Al-Fanar Media</strong>, I build
          digital products for one of the Arab world's leading independent news organisations,
          covering education, research, and culture across the region. I understand what it
          means to build for real users with real impact.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-stone-600">
          My background in finance taught me to think in systems, work under pressure, and
          communicate clearly across teams. I bring those instincts into every project I touch.
        </p>

        <!-- Values pills -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-2">
          {
            [
              "Impact-driven",
              "Bilingual (AR/EN)",
              "Cross-industry perspective",
              "User-first thinking",
            ].map((tag) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-bone-300 bg-serenade-50 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-stone-700">
                {tag}
              </span>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right — Highlight cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {
          [
            {
              icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>`,
              title: "Web Development",
              body: "Crafting modern, performant web experiences with a focus on clean architecture and user experience.",
              bg: "bg-stone-800",
              text: "text-stone-100",
              accent: "text-honey-200",
            },
            {
              icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4Z"/></svg>`,
              title: "Business Analysis",
              body: "Years in financial services sharpened my ability to define requirements, spot inefficiencies, and align tech with business goals.",
              bg: "bg-cream-100",
              text: "text-stone-800",
              accent: "text-honey-200",
            },
            {
              icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>`,
              title: "Client Relationships",
              body: "Managing complex stakeholder relationships across banking and media has made clear communication second nature.",
              bg: "bg-serenade-50",
              text: "text-stone-800",
              accent: "text-stone-600",
            },
            {
              icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>`,
              title: "Bilingual & Global",
              body: "Native Arabic and fluent English speaker — bridging the gap between Western tech and Arab-world audiences.",
              bg: "bg-minty-100/40",
              text: "text-stone-800",
              accent: "text-stone-600",
            },
          ].map((card) => (
            <div
              class={`flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl p-6 ${card.bg}`}
            >
              <div class={`${card.accent}`} set:html={card.icon} />
              <div>
                <h3 class={`mb-1.5 font-semibold ${card.text}`}>{card.title}</h3>
                <p class={`text-sm leading-relaxed ${card.text === "text-stone-100" ? "text-stone-400" : "text-stone-600"}`}>
                  {card.body}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
